title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1987-09-23
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi DR-1) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) >KORG AudioGate 4 > Adobe Audition CC 2015 > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC/24
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger -> Franklin's Tower, Walkin' Blues, Friend Of The Devil, Tons Of Steel -> Desolation Row, Big Railroad Blues -> The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Bertha-> Cumberland Blues, Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Playin' In The Band Jam-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Around & Around-> Good Lovin'-> La Bamba-> Good Lovin', E: U.S. Blues
